    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.T.) *Anno ab incarnatione domini nostri Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo
                        sesto,* indicione terciadecima. Quę ad honorem ęclesiarum et fidelium
                        catholicorum sustentationem erogantur, quin in centuplum recompensentur et
                        quod melius est vita retribuatur ęterna, nulli prorsus fidelium dubitandum
                        est: et maxime monasteriis que in nostris possessionibus constituta sunt et
                        religiosis viris qui ibi Deo famulantur: si in necessitatibus viscera
                        pietatis recludamus, quomodo hcaritas Dei erit in nobis? Ideoque ego
                            <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Beneficium #Islands #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Shores #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Forests #Cereals #Legumes #Hay/fodder #Animals"
                            ref="#people/125">Matilda</persName> Dei gratia quicquid sum, pro
                        mercede et remedio animae meae parentumque meorum, <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Offersio/donatio #Islands #Fisheries #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Shores #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Forests #Cereals #Legumes #Hay/fodder #Animals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti sito inter <placeName
                                ref="#places/4196" key="#Rivers">Padum</placeName> et <placeName
                                ref="#places/4197" key="#Rivers">Larionem</placeName></orgName> ubi
                        nunc donnus <persName key="Abbots" ref="#people/2189">Albericus</persName>
                        <rs key="Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, concedo a presenti die in
                        perpetuum quicquid <persName key="#Beneficium"><name
                                ref="Gherardus/de Sancto Benedicto">Gerardus</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/2400">Sancto Benedicto</placeName> a me in <rs
                            key="#Beneficium">beneficium</rs> triduo ante mortem suam detinebat, et
                        quicquid ab abbate de <placeName key="Abbots" ref="#places/2485"
                            >Brixillo</placeName> per commutationem adquisivi, tam in loco Sancti
                        Benedicti quam in <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/80"><rs
                                key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/362"
                            >Villole</placeName></geogName>, ita ut predictum monasterium habeat,
                        possideat, fruatur; et abbas qui pro tempore fuerit faciat inde quicquid ei
                        utile visum fuerit, sine mea et heredum meorum contradictione, omni michi
                        circa easdem res potestate exclusa. Preterea per hanc meae <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">donationis paginam</rs> eidem monasterio concedo
                        quicquid michi pertinet in <rs key="#Islands">insula</rs> Sancti Benedicti
                        et in curte Villolę, cum omni iure quod ad ipsas possesiones pertinet: cum
                            <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries"
                            >piscationibus</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venationibus</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Legumes">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pascuis</rs>, aquis, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquarum usibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Shores">ripis</rs> et <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs> cum
                        accessionibus et ingressibus seu cum superioribus et inferioribus suis in
                        integrum, ea tamen racione ut pars prefati monasterii post meum decessum
                        habeat, teneat, possideat et faciat quicquid exinde voluerit; nec michi
                        liceat ullo tempore mutare quod volui, sed quod a me semel factum et
                        conscriptum est inviolabile et firmum permaneat. Ut autem in poste[rum de
                        finibus] nulla dubitatio sit per hos fines decernantur: scilicet insula
                        Sancti Benedicti a mane et meridie habet fines <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvium</rs> Padi, a sera curtem de <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2095">Runco Rolandi</geogName> et curtem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2099">Saviolę</geogName>, a septentrione
                        fluvium Larionem. Villola habet a mane fines aggerem antiquum; a sera
                            <placeName key="#Forests" ref="#places/4194">silvam que dicitur
                            Castagnola</placeName>, et <placeName key="#Forests" ref="#places/4193"
                            >silva Solamen</placeName>, et <placeName ref="#places/4192"
                            >Carpeneta</placeName>, et sicut percurrit Rivolus usque in Piscarolam;
                        a meridie fossa Piscarola usque in Perotolam, a septentrione fluvium Padi et
                        in parte terra Sancti Benedicti. Similiter per hanc meę offersionis paginam
                        confirmo et corroboro quicquid in supradictum monasterium a parentibus meis
                        collatum est ut habeat pleno iure, tam ex parentum meorum liberalitate quam
                        ex mea voluntaria confirmatione: hoc est medietas insule Sancti Benedicti,
                        et pars quedam in Villola, et <placeName ref="#places/2929">Caput de
                            Vico</placeName>, curtem <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2007"
                            >Clustelli</geogName>, curtem <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/2083">Septingenti</geogName>, <placeName
                            ref="#places/2931">Casale Barbati</placeName>, et pars quedam in
                            <placeName ref="#places/482">Burbassio</placeName> et omnia quęcumque a
                        parentibus meis quocumque titulo data vel concessa sunt in eodem venerabili
                        loco. In omnibus autem que supra scripta sunt non habeat aliquam potestatem
                        neque dux neque marchio, comes aut vicecomes, gastaldius vel decanus,
                        postremo nulla parva aut magna persona, sed omnia libera sint ab omni
                        exactione et publica functione propter mercede et remedio anime meę et
                        parentum meorum. Quod si quis contra hec agere temptaverit, et temerario
                        ausu quę supra comprehensa sunt irruperit, <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi
                            libras decem</rs> componat, medietatem venerabili loco et medietatem <rs
                            key="#Camera">parti publicę</rs>. Quod ut melius credatur et ab omnibus
                        firmius teneatur, manus meę subnotatione firmavi. Hactum est hoc in <rs
                            key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/145">Nogarię</placeName>, tercio
                        kalendas ianuarias, presente <persName
                            key="#Bishops #Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/2190"
                            >Ugone</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/275">Mantuano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs>. Matilda Dei gratia si quid est subscripsi.
                            <rs key="#Count">Comes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count #Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/2196">Vuido
                            Werra</persName> interfuit <rs key="#Witness">testis</rs>. Comes
                            <persName key="#Count #Witness #Offersio/donatio #childOf"
                            ref="#people/2197">Albertus</persName>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Boso">Bosonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #childOf" ref="#people/3500"
                            >Ardoinus</persName>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Wido">Vuidonis</name></persName>
                        filius, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #childOf"><name
                                ref="Gherardus/f. Bosonis">Gerardus</name></persName>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Boso">Bosonis</name></persName> filius,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #childOf" ref="#people/2199"
                            >Ugo</persName>
                        <persName key="#parentOf" ref="#people/3510">Manfredi</persName> filius,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #cousinOf" ref="#people/2193"
                            >Saxo</persName> et <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio #cousinOf"
                            ref="#people/2198">Rainerius</persName>
                        <rs key="#cousinOf">consobrinus</rs> eius, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3515">Nordilus de Castello
                            Vetere</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            ref="#people/3516">Lanfrancus de Savignano</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3517">Opizo de
                            Gunzaga</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            ref="#people/3519">Rainerius de Castro Olariano</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3521">Albericus de
                            Nonantula</persName> interfuerunt testes. (S.) Ego <persName
                            key="Writer #Offersio/donatio Judge" ref="#people/2185"
                            >Ubaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="Judge">iudex</rs> manu mea <rs key="Writer">scripsi</rs> hanc
                        concessionem et post traditam complevi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
